    "title": "10 Prompting Tips for Video Generation: Create Stunning AI Videos",
    "slug": "10-prompting-tips-video-generation",
    "metaDescription": "Master AI video generation with 10 expert prompting tips. Learn how to create stunning videos using AI tools with quality control optimization for professional results.",
    "date": "March 23, 2026",
    "readTime": "9 min read",
    "intro": "Creating amazing AI videos goes beyond simple text-to-video prompts. These 10 expert tips will help you master video generation prompting, from basic concepts to advanced techniques. Each tip includes quality control (Q.C.) optimization to ensure professional results every time.",

    "tip1Title": "1. Define Identity (Activate Persona)",
    "tip1Content": "**Start with character and identity definition**. The robot touches a virtual screen, and a holographic 'Character Creator' interface appears. The Nano Banana mascot materializes with adjustable sliders for 'Flavor: Vanilla,' 'Size: Nano,' and 'Origin: Cyber-Farm.' **Q.C. Check**: Does your prompt clearly define the main character's visual identity and attributes?",

    "tip2Title": "2. Highlight Benefits (Showcase Value)",
    "tip2Content": "**Use spotlight effects to emphasize key value propositions**. A digital spotlight sweeps across three floating pedestals that rise with dynamic text tags: 'NUTRITION,' 'CONVENIENCE,' and 'SUSTAINABILITY.' When spotlight hits 'Convenience,' animate a hand quickly grabbing the Nano Banana while running. **Q.C. Check**: Have you specified lighting effects that highlight your product's key benefits?",

    "tip3Title": "3. Specify Audience (Target Demographics)",
    "tip3Content": "**Create holographic radar/map animations for audience targeting**. A holographic radar pulses with dots labeled 'MILLENNIALS,' 'FOODIES,' and 'PARENTS.' Data streams connect these points to the central Nano Banana profile. **Q.C. Check**: Does your prompt include visual elements that represent your target demographics?",

    "tip4Title": "4. Set Tone & Style (Choose Voice)",
    "tip4Content": "**Use mixing board interfaces for tone control**. A mixing board appears with knobs for 'Wit,' 'Fun,' and 'Information.' As knobs turn, background lighting changes from cool blue (professional) to warm yellow (fun). **Q.C. Check**: Have you specified color grading and lighting that match your desired tone?",

    "tip5Title": "5. Use Storytelling (Craft Narrative)",
    "tip5Content": "**Create animated narrative sequences**. A holographic book opens with animated landscape where Nano Banana is the 'hero' jumping over obstacles (digital broccoli) on a quest toward a kitchen counter. Include speech bubbles or subtitles for narrative context. **Q.C. Check**: Does your video prompt include a clear story arc with hero journey elements?",

    "tip6Title": "6. Inject Metaphors (Create Comparisons)",
    "tip6Content": "**Use visual scale metaphors for concept illustration**. A digital scale appears weighing Nano Banana against an oversized old-fashioned clock to illustrate 'Efficiency.' Use unexpected visual comparisons to make abstract concepts concrete. **Q.C. Check**: Have you included visual metaphors that enhance understanding of complex ideas?",

    "tip7Title": "7. Add Sensory Details (Evoke Senses)",
    "tip7Content": "**Incorporate multi-sensory animation effects**. As a hand peels the banana, add animated 'scent' lines (aroma), sparkling 'light' lines (texture), and visual 'snap' effect (sound). Use particle effects and motion graphics to evoke multiple senses. **Q.C. Check**: Does your prompt include sensory visual effects like particles, glows, and motion trails?",

    "tip8Title": "8. Structure Content (Create Workflow)",
    "tip8Content": "**Design interface animations for content organization**. Show a tablet with clean timeline where elements are dragged into perfect order: 'INTRO,' 'BENEFITS,' 'RECIPES,' 'CONCLUSION.' Add progress bars that populate as each section locks in. **Q.C. Check**: Have you specified UI/UX elements that demonstrate structured content flow?",

    "tip9Title": "9. Diversify Formats (Show Variety)",
    "tip9Content": "**Create multi-screen format variety animations**. Multiple screens spin into view showing different output types: scrolling listicle, cooking video with recipe interface, and chat transcript. Use dynamic screen transitions to showcase content versatility. **Q.C. Check**: Does your prompt include varied visual formats and screen layouts?",

    "tip10Title": "10. Refine & Iterate (Optimization Loop)",
    "tip10Content": "**Animate the optimization process visually**. Show arrow/pencil icon moving along curved loop where final product goes through stylized 'scanner' that highlights weak sections. Robot uses pencil to draw corrections, and loop pulses again showing optimized result. **Q.C. Check**: Have you described the iterative improvement process with visual feedback loops?",

